title: LibGuides: Complementary Medicine: Resources
author: Julia Hendricks
description: Complementary medicine, Chinese medicine, Herbal medicine Resources for research
cleaned_text: Use the [E-resources A-Z](https://libguides.westminster.ac.uk/az.php) to see all of our resources by subject and type. You can access most of them off-campus using your University username and password or by selecting Institutional Login and choosing University of Westminster from the drop-down list.
